<A NAME="ref-chapter-BGL"></A><h1>CGAL and the Boost Graph Library<BR>
<I>Reference&nbsp;Manual</I></h1>
<P>

<p class="subtitle">Andreas Fabri, Fernando Cacciola, and Ron Wein</p>
<P>

This chapter introduces the concepts and classes that allow to interface <span class="textsc">Cgal</span> data structures 
with the algorithms of the <span class="textsc">Bgl</span>, as well as a new graph concept.
<P>

